metadata.name: Pepe Mecha Lab
metadata.description:
This is the Genesis of DXX58 on the ETH blockchain - FND. 

PNG 3000 x 3000 px

==============

The planet is in imminent danger. Scientists are in a hurry to quickly create giant robots to protect the planet from the attacks of creatures called Humon.

This mecha is named P3P3. A gigantic robot with great punching power that can tear down walls as thick as 1 meter with ease. P3P3 has a source of energy from the spirit of the citizens of the planet stored in its chest.

The best pepe scientists were mobilized to ensure this project ran smoothly. A black cat is involved to give extra luck in planetary protection efforts.
